umber gambar: facebook.com/plantlilycosplayer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18348\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-13.jpg\" alt=\"Plant Lily. Cosplayer Vietnam yang berdomisili di Singapore. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/plantlilycosplayer\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18348\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Plant Lily. Cosplayer Vietnam yang berdomisili di Singapore. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/plantlilycosplayer</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hadir pula Zainaru &amp; Rian CYD dari team cosplayer professional Jakarta “Daikon Sky”. Daikon Sky sendiri sudah lebih dulu dikenal sebagai team cosplayer papan atas Indonesia dan sudah sering diundang menghadiri event cosplay di luar negeri.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18363\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18363\" data-attachment-id=\"18363\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-18.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Zainaru. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/zainaruhouse\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Zainaru. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/zainaruhouse&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-18.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-18.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18363\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-18.jpg\" alt=\"Zainaru. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/zainaruhouse\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18363\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zainaru. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/zainaruhouse</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Berlangsung selama dua hari berturut-turut dengan harga tiket masuk pre-sale sebesar IDR 35.000 (on-spot IDR 50.000), Little Akihabara menyajikan beragam hal!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18345\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18345\" data-attachment-id=\"18345\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Pre-sale ticket voucher. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Pre-sale ticket voucher. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18345\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-12.jpg\" alt=\"Pre-sale ticket voucher. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18345\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pre-sale ticket voucher. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Misalnya booth-booth yang menjual berbagai pernak-pernik manga dan anime seperti gantungan kunci, poster, sticker dan lainnya. Ada juga booth dari toko buku besar seperti Gramedia dan brand produk komputer terkenal MSI.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18333\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18333\" data-attachment-id=\"18333\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Foto dari sudut pintu masuk Hall. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Foto dari sudut pintu masuk Hall. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-8.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18333\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-8.jpg\" alt=\"Foto dari sudut pintu masuk Hall. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18333\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Foto dari sudut pintu masuk Hall. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Menurut salah satu pengunjung bernama Patricia, <em>layout booth</em> ini terkesan tidak rapi dan cukup berantakan, akan lebih keren kalau posisi booth-booth ini mengelilingi venue dengan menyisakan ruang lebih lega di tengah untuk pengunjung lewat.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18336\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18336\" data-attachment-id=\"18336\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Lumayan rada semak sih memang…. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Lumayan rada semak sih memang…. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-9.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18336\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-9.jpg\" alt=\"Lumayan rada semak sih memang…. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18336\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lumayan rada semak sih memang…. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebelumnya saya juga sempat berbincang singkat dengan salah satu perwakilan dari panitia, Merryn, yang berharap jika acara ini dapat menjembatani antara para fans J-Pop culture seperti cosplay dan fans gaming online/e-sport agar dapat bergembira bersama. Pihak GLOW Enterprise sebagai EO memang berkomitmen memberikan suatu hiburan yang menyenangkan buat para pengunjung yang datang ke acara mereka.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ada juga Maid Café, spot dimana pengunjung café akan mendapatkan <em>treatment</em> seperti maid café yang ada di wilayah Akihabara, Jepang. Maid Café sendiri merupakan atraksi yang populer karena unik dan seru dengan maid yang cantik berseragam khas maid (biasanya berupa variasi dari seragam <em>french maid</em>).</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18390\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18390\" data-attachment-id=\"18390\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Pengunjung Maid Café yang disambut meriah. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/chenrouxiu\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Pengunjung Maid Café yang disambut meriah. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/chenrouxiu&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-6.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18390\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-6.jpg\" alt=\"Pengunjung Maid Café yang disambut meriah. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/chenrouxiu\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18390\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pengunjung Maid Café yang disambut meriah. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/chenrouxiu</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di hari pertama ada perlombaan menyanyi lagu Jepang serta Seiyuu Contest yang seru sekali. Seiyuu Contest adalah sebuah pertandingan dimana para peserta menggunakan suara mereka untuk menggantikan suara yang ada di dalam anime.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Workshop singkat dari dua member Daikon Sky, Naru dan Rian, berhasil menarik perhatian para pengunkung, workshop berisi cara <em>molding</em> atau membentuk bahan bernama Worbla, bahan termoplastik yang dapat dimanfaatkan sebagai bahan pembuat kostum cosplay seperti bahan yang sudah lebih dulu biasa digunakan para <em>costume maker</em>, yaitu busa hati.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18339\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18339\" data-attachment-id=\"18339\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Workshop dari Naru &#038; Rian. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Workshop dari Naru &#038; Rian. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-10.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18339\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-10.jpg\" alt=\"Workshop dari Naru &amp; Rian. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18339\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Workshop dari Naru &amp; Rian. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano</p></div>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Day-2</strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hari kedua merupakan puncak acara dari Little Akihabara. Perbedaan jumlah pengunjung hari kedua dibandingkan hari pertama terlihat cukup signifikan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18342\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18342\" data-attachment-id=\"18342\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mendadak meluber. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mendadak meluber. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-11.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18342\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-11.jpg\" alt=\"Mendadak meluber. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18342\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mendadak meluber. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Selain final lomba e-sport DotA dan AOV yang digelar sejak hari pertama, di hari kedua ini juga digelar lomba utama, yaitu lomba perform cosplay.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lomba ini memang sudah seperti puncak acara di event J-Pop culture mana saja di kota Medan (dan mungkin juga di kota-kota lain). Kali ini terasa spesial karena team juri yang akan menilai merupakan nama-nama besar dan tidak asing di dunia cosplay nasional serta internasional.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Frea Mai sebagai costume maker professional, Naru dan Rian sebagai cosplayer yang sudah malang melintang di dunia cosplay Indonesia sejak lama, serta Plant Lily sebagai cosplayer internasional bergabung untuk menilai kostum dan performance para cosplayer Medan yanng hadir di acara Little Akihabara.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18399\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18399\" data-attachment-id=\"18399\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-15-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-15-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Plant Lily, Frea Mai &#038; V Kanon. MC Darius Drew. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Plant Lily, Frea Mai &#038; V Kanon. MC Darius Drew. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-15-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-15-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18399\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-15-1.jpg\" alt=\"Plant Lily, Frea Mai &amp; V Kanon. MC Darius Drew. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18399\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Plant Lily, Frea Mai &amp; V Kanon. MC Darius Drew. Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Para peserta lomba dituntut menampilkan performance terbaik mereka agar mendapatkan penilaian positif dari team juri. Akhirnya “Team Angin Sepoi-Sepoi” yang melakukan kabaret Naruto berhasil menyabet gelar juara di lomba perform cosplay di acara ini. Pertunjukan mereka membuat baik penonton maupun para juri tertawa dan melakukan <em>standing ovation</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ke depannya tentu para fans J-Pop culture berharap agar acara seperti ini semakin sering diadakan di kota Medan. Semoga saja EO seperti GLOW Enterprise kembali mengadakan acara sekaliber Little Akihabara 2017 di waktu yang akan datang.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18351\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18351\" data-attachment-id=\"18351\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/little-akihabara-2017-medan-sumatera-utara/attachment/isi-akihabara-x-320-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-14.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"isi akihabara x 320 14\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mentalitas orang Indonesia mungkin sulit untuk diubah? Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-14.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-14.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18351\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-akihabara-x-320-14.jpg\" alt=\"Mentalitas orang Indonesia mungkin sulit untuk diubah? Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18351\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mentalitas orang Indonesia mungkin sulit untuk diubah? Sumber gambar: facebook.com/HarryRezqiano</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sayangnya kebiasaan orang Indonesia yang ‘rajin’ buang sampah sembarangan tetap terlihat. Bahkan di event dengan tiket masuk seperti ini. Hal ini sangat disesalkan mengingat bagaimana orang Jepang yang sadar kebersihan, dan acara yang berlangsung sedikit banyak bernuansa kebudayaan Jepang juga.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"27b6e192-579b-5fce-9bae-a05ba92d97a6"}}}